    public class OptionsFormElementBuilder
extends com.foreach.across.modules.web.ui.elements.builder.AbstractNodeViewElementBuilder<com.foreach.across.modules.web.ui.elements.AbstractNodeViewElement,OptionsFormElementBuilder>
    Responsible for building option lists as SELECT, RADIO, TOGGLE or MULTI CHECKBOX. Takes a collection of OptionFormElementBuilders and will apply the global type to them, no matter what type they were originally defined with.
    Author:
    Arne Vandamme
    See Also:
    OptionFormElementBuilder
